Package org.neo4j.internal.recordstorage

Class SchemaCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.internal.recordstorage.SchemaCache
  • public class SchemaCache
extends Object
    A cache of schema rules as well as enforcement of schema consistency. Will always reflect the committed state of the schema store.
